title: Jihosoft Phone Transfer 3.4.2 - SeuPirate
description:
Jihosoft Phone Transfer 3.4.2 - SeuPirate

Jihosoft Phone Data Transfer helps you transfer photos, videos, music, contacts, SMS, call logs, calendars, etc. between Android and iOS device by one click.

Popular Android and iOS Devices Supported
Samsung: Samsung Galaxy S8 (+), S7 (Edge) / S6 (Edge) / S5 / S4, Galaxy Note 7 / 5/ 4, etc.
HTC: HTC U11 / U Ultra / U Play / Bolt, HTC One X10 / One S9, etc.
Huawei: Huawei P10 / P9 / P8, Huawei Honor 8, etc.
Sony: Sony Xperia XZ1, Xperia XZ1 Compact, Xperia XZ Premium, etc.
LG: LG V30+, LG V30, LG Q8, LG Q6a, LG G6 / G5, etc.
Motorola: Motorola Moto E4 Plus, Moto E4, Moto G5 Plus, etc.
Google: Google Nexus 6P / 6, Google Nexus 5X / 5, Google Nexus 10, etc.
iPhone: iPhone X / 8 / 7 (Plus) / SE / 6S (Plus) / 6 (Plus) / 5S / 5 / 5C, etc.
iPad: iPad Pro, iPad Mini 4, iPad 4 / 3 / 2, iPad with Retina display, the New iPad, etc.
iPod: iPod touch 6, 5, 4, iPod Nano, iPod Shuffle, iPod Mini, iPod Classic

Excellent Tool for Managing Your Mobile Data
Different Transfer Modes: This phone transfer tool has 2 different transfer modes; one is Phone to Phone transfer, another is iTunes to Phone transfer. So you can flexibly transfer data between phones or transfer data from iTunes backup to Android/iOS mobiles.
Backup&Restore Phone Data: Through this tool, you can backup and restore Android data on computer; Meanwhile, you can also restore backup files from other source like iTunes, Phone Recovery, Phone Manager.

Security&Efficiency for Phone Transfer
High Efficiency: Jihosoft Phone Transfer will only transfer the selected data you want; moreover, the transfer speed is very fast, which will be very time-saving.
100% Security: This transfer tool only reads and transfers the data you’ve chosen and the transferred data is 100% the same as the original one. No data will be damaged and leaked.

Homepage: http://www.jihosoft.com/mobile/phone-transfer.html

By:

SeuPirate
